					<div class="stl_01" style="left:13.5em;top:33.409em;"><span class="stl_39" style="word-spacing:0.74em;">(1) </span><span class="stl_40 stl_09" style="word-spacing:0.78em;">A public hearing to receive comments; and </span><span class="stl_39 stl_09" style="word-spacing:0.78em;">(2) </span><span class="stl_40 stl_11" style="word-spacing:0.73em;">consideratio<span class="stl_09">n of &nbsp;</span></span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="left:13.5em;top:34.559em;"><span class="stl_40" style="word-spacing:0.43em;">authorizing a public hearing to amend Chapter 51A, “Dallas Development &nbsp;</span></div>
