					<div class="stl_01" style="left:4.5625em;top:33.3909em;"><span class="stl_41 stl_09" style="word-spacing:0.44em;">PH2. </span><a href="https://cityofdallas.legistar.com/gateway.aspx?m=l&amp;id=/matter.aspx?key=24590" target="_blank"><span class="stl_47">26-1456A &nbsp;</span></a></div>
